                  signal="Announce")
public void Announce(short version,
                                        short port,
                                        BusObjectDescription[] objectDescriptions,
                                        Map<String,Variant> aboutData)
        Signal handler
        Specified by:
        Announce in interface AboutTransport
        Parameters:
        version - The interface version is added since it might help with the decision to connect back.
        port - The global gateway port for the services for this application
        objectDescriptions - Descriptions of the BusObjects that make up the service. "a(sas)"
        aboutData - Service specific key/value pairs. (Service implementers are free to populate this dictionary with any key/value pairs that are meaningful to the service and its potential consumers) "a{sv}"
